' RELACIONES - FRONTEND ADMIN → BACKEND
' ===============================================

AngularAdmin --> HTTPS : REST calls /api/v1/admin/*
DashboardAdmin --> AdminApiService
UserManagement --> AdminApiService
RoleManagement --> AdminApiService
PermissionManagement --> AdminApiService
SubscriptionManagement --> AdminApiService
AuditLogsModule --> AdminApiService

AdminAuthService --> HTTPS : POST /api/v1/auth/*
AdminApiService --> HTTPS : /api/v1/admin/*

AdminGuards ..> AdminAuthService : Check admin permissions
AdminInterceptors ..> HTTPS : JWT + Error handling

AngularAdmin ..> TailwindShared : Styles
AngularAdmin ..> CommonComponents : UI components
AdminApiService ..> RxJSUtils : Observables

' ===============================================
' RELACIONES - FRONTEND CLIENTE → BACKEND
' ===============================================

AngularClient --> HTTPS : REST calls /api/v1/app/*
DashboardUsuario --> ClientApiService
CalendarioModule --> ClientApiService
TareasModule --> ClientApiService
NotificacionesModule --> ClientApiService
ArchivosModule --> ClientApiService
PortafolioModule --> ClientApiService
CompartidosModule --> ClientApiService

ClientAuthService --> HTTPS : POST /api/v1/auth/*
ClientApiService --> HTTPS : /api/v1/app/*

ClientGuards ..> ClientAuthService : Check auth
ClientGuards ..> FeatureGateService : Check plan features
ClientInterceptors ..> HTTPS : JWT + Error handling

AngularClient ..> TailwindShared : Styles
AngularClient ..> CommonComponents : UI components
ClientApiService ..> RxJSUtils : Observables

' ===============================================
' RELACIONES - SHARED LIBRARIES
' ===============================================

AngularAdmin ..> CommonModels : Shared interfaces
AngularClient ..> CommonModels : Shared interfaces

