JWTMiddleware --> TenantMiddleware : 2. Set tenant context
TenantMiddleware --> PermissionMiddleware : 3. Load user permissions
PermissionMiddleware --> SharePermissionMiddleware : 4. Check share access
SharePermissionMiddleware --> FeatureGateMiddleware : 5. Check plan features
FeatureGateMiddleware --> RateLimitMiddleware : 6. Rate limit by plan
RateLimitMiddleware --> TenantsAPI : 7. Route to endpoint

' Admin API endpoints
TenantsAPI --> RBACService
UsersAPI --> RBACService
RolesAPI --> RBACService
PermissionsAPI --> RBACService
SubscriptionsAPI --> BackendBillingService
AuditAPI --> RBACService
AnalyticsAPI --> RBACService

