PgBouncer --> PostgreSQL

ORM --> PostgresProtocol : SQL queries
Signals ..> PostgresProtocol : Trigger actions
ShareService --> PostgresProtocol : CRUD shares
PermissionInheritanceEngine --> PostgresProtocol : Recursive permission queries

PostgreSQL --> Tables
